<tr>
<td style="padding-top:0.2em; padding-bottom:0.2em;">
<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none; padding:0;">
<div class="NavHead" style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF3399; padding-left:0.3em; background:transparent; text-align:left; color:#FF3399;">Precursors</div>
<div class="NavContent" style="padding:0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align:center; display:inline;"><a href="/wiki/Age_of_Enlightenment" title="Age of Enlightenment">Age of Enlightenment</a><br />
